data.title: Iowa City School District
data.text:
We've got a vibrant community here in the Iowa City Community School District â€“ over 14,000 awesome students and counting! We're actually the fourth biggest school district in Iowa. Cool, right? Here you can dive into the unique opportunities we have to offer, stay in the loop with the latest news and calendar updates, meet our administrative team, and a whole lot more! Happy exploring!

We are committed to providing supports that allow for all students to reach their full potential. Here you will find information on our specialized education services, our mental health supports, our community connections, and more. We are here for you!

Our goal is to provide dynamic learning opportunities and future-focused educational programming. Here you will discover the depth and breadth of our academic offerings and our unique programming opportunities that prepare students to be college, career, and life ready. Ready to explore?

At the heart of everything we do are our amazing students and families. We've got all the info and resources you need, from enrollment to school meals to transportation and everything in between. We've got you covered!
